[SPEAKER_00] radi nedjeljom.

396
00:17:50,819 --> 00:17:53,700
[SPEAKER_00] Onda djece nemaju ručka,

397
00:17:53,700 --> 00:17:55,680
[SPEAKER_00] onda obitelj nije zajedno na okupu.

398
00:17:57,039 --> 00:17:57,720
[SPEAKER_00] Istina je,

399
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] neke ustanove

400
00:17:59,599 --> 00:18:01,440
[SPEAKER_00] moraju raditi nedjeljom.

401
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:05,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovo što se danas događa,

402
00:18:05,019 --> 00:18:06,259
[SPEAKER_00] znak je

403
00:18:06,259 --> 00:18:08,319
[SPEAKER_00] da nas je neko potaknuo

404
00:18:08,319 --> 00:18:09,680
[SPEAKER_00] da budemo bezbožni.

405
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] A mi na to ne bismo smijeli pristati.

406
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:16,140
[SPEAKER_00] I jedan dobar autor,

407
00:18:16,140 --> 00:18:17,319
[SPEAKER_00] vjerujem da ste čitali,

408
00:18:17,319 --> 00:18:19,259
[SPEAKER_00] barem njegovu gozbu Jagančevu,

409
00:18:19,259 --> 00:18:20,299
[SPEAKER_00] zove se Scott Hahn,

410
00:18:20,299 --> 00:18:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] kako tumači ono iz knjiga otkrivenja

411
00:18:23,460 --> 00:18:24,319
[SPEAKER_00] broj 666,

412
00:18:24,319 --> 00:18:26,240
[SPEAKER_00] tri šestice,

413
00:18:26,359 --> 00:18:27,799
[SPEAKER_00] koji je broj Sotone,

414
00:18:27,799 --> 00:18:29,619
[SPEAKER_00] zloga duha.

415
00:18:29,619 --> 00:18:31,579
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže

416
00:18:31,579 --> 00:18:34,400
[SPEAKER_00] kako su čovjek

417
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:36,200
[SPEAKER_00] i zvijer

418
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] stvoreni u šesti dan,

419
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] ali čovjek je stvoren

420
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:41,180
[SPEAKER_00] za sedmi dan,

421
00:18:41,180 --> 00:18:43,220
[SPEAKER_00] kada Bog gleda

422
00:18:43,220 --> 00:18:44,160
[SPEAKER_00] i divi se

423
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:45,859
[SPEAKER_00] kako je to sve dobro

424
00:18:45,859 --> 00:18:47,299
[SPEAKER_00] i lijepo načinio.

425
00:18:47,299 --> 00:18:48,859
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže

426
00:18:48,859 --> 00:18:51,059
[SPEAKER_00] kada čovjek

427
00:18:51,059 --> 00:18:52,180
[SPEAKER_00] ne dolazi

428
00:18:52,180 --> 00:18:53,420
[SPEAKER_00] do tog sedmog dana,

429
00:18:53,420 --> 00:18:54,299
[SPEAKER_00] to jest kada

430
00:18:54,299 --> 00:18:55,559
[SPEAKER_00] pukne veza

431
00:18:55,559 --> 00:18:56,759
[SPEAKER_00] sa njegovim Bogom,

432
00:18:56,759 --> 00:18:57,940
[SPEAKER_00] sa našim stvoriteljem

433
00:18:57,940 --> 00:18:58,740
[SPEAKER_00] i spasiteljem

434
00:18:58,740 --> 00:18:59,880
[SPEAKER_00] Isusom Kristom,

435
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:01,779
[SPEAKER_00] što se tada događa?

436
00:19:02,180 --> 00:19:03,700
[SPEAKER_00] Da čovjek zapne

437
00:19:03,700 --> 00:19:05,619
[SPEAKER_00] u šestom danu,

438
00:19:05,619 --> 00:19:07,180
[SPEAKER_00] a šesti dan

439
00:19:07,180 --> 00:19:09,160
[SPEAKER_00] je dan zvijeri.

440
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:12,019
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome,

441
00:19:12,019 --> 00:19:16,819
[SPEAKER_00] evo i Božja riječ,

442
00:19:16,819 --> 00:19:18,160
[SPEAKER_00] a i ovaj dobar komentar,

443
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:19,900
[SPEAKER_00] poticaj su

444
00:19:19,900 --> 00:19:21,740
[SPEAKER_00] ne kupovati

445
00:19:21,740 --> 00:19:23,839
[SPEAKER_00] niti prodavati

446
00:19:23,839 --> 00:19:24,420
[SPEAKER_00] nedeljom.

447
00:19:24,420 --> 00:19:26,660
[SPEAKER_00] Rad je svet,

448
00:19:26,660 --> 00:19:29,019
[SPEAKER_00] ali on postaje zlo

449
00:19:29,019 --> 00:19:31,160
[SPEAKER_00] ako čovjek odbija ga

450
00:19:31,160 --> 00:19:32,220
[SPEAKER_00] prikazati Bogu.

451
00:19:32,220 --> 00:19:32,880
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodine,

452
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:33,980
[SPEAKER_00] evo ovo

453
00:19:33,980 --> 00:19:36,839
[SPEAKER_00] ovo se dogodilo

454
00:19:36,839 --> 00:19:37,559
[SPEAKER_00] u ovom tjednu,

455
00:19:37,559 --> 00:19:38,559
[SPEAKER_00] činio sam to i to,

456
00:19:38,559 --> 00:19:39,740
[SPEAKER_00] ali kada dolazim

457
00:19:39,740 --> 00:19:40,500
[SPEAKER_00] na svetu misu,

458
00:19:40,500 --> 00:19:41,819
[SPEAKER_00] želim ti to prikazati,

459
00:19:41,819 --> 00:19:42,759
[SPEAKER_00] želim to staviti

460
00:19:42,759 --> 00:19:43,440
[SPEAKER_00] na oltar,

461
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] želim da ti to

462
00:19:44,599 --> 00:19:45,539
[SPEAKER_00] preobraziš

463
00:19:45,539 --> 00:19:46,200
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno

464
00:19:46,200 --> 00:19:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] blagosloviš.

465
00:19:47,380 --> 00:19:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] Evo vidite,

466
00:19:48,380 --> 00:19:49,539
[SPEAKER_00] sveci me uvijek

467
00:19:49,539 --> 00:19:50,420
[SPEAKER_00] fasciniraju,

468
00:19:51,059 --> 00:19:52,500
[SPEAKER_00] naprimjer sveti Benedikt

469
00:19:52,500 --> 00:19:55,339
[SPEAKER_00] koji je u temeljima Evrope,

470
00:19:55,339 --> 00:19:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] on je rekao

471
00:19:57,039 --> 00:19:58,779
[SPEAKER_00] osam sati radi,

472
00:19:58,779 --> 00:20:00,460
[SPEAKER_00] osam sati moli

473
00:20:00,460 --> 00:20:03,400
[SPEAKER_00] i osam sati se odmaraji.

474
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] I nekako je to ostalo.

475
00:20:04,619 --> 00:20:05,799
[SPEAKER_00] Znademo da bi radno vrijeme

476
00:20:05,799 --> 00:20:06,160
[SPEAKER_00] trebalo

477
00:20:06,160 --> 00:20:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] trebati osam sati.

478
00:20:07,619 --> 00:20:08,839
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko trebamo spavat?

479
00:20:08,839 --> 00:20:11,339
[SPEAKER_00] Osam sati.

480
00:20:11,339 --> 00:20:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko vi spavate?

481
00:20:12,119 --> 00:20:14,079
[SPEAKER_00] Čuo sam neki od vas deset čak.

482
00:20:14,079 --> 00:20:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] To sam isto negdje.

483
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:19,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ali neki spavaju jako malo.

484
00:20:19,900 --> 00:20:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome vidiš Benedikta

485
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:23,140
[SPEAKER_00] koji je ono vrijeme

486
00:20:23,140 --> 00:20:25,180
[SPEAKER_00] dao jedan,

487
00:20:25,180 --> 00:20:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno Bog je po njemu dao

488
00:20:27,539 --> 00:20:29,400
[SPEAKER_00] jedan žar duha Evropi.

489
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:31,619
[SPEAKER_00] Da je nastala jedna lijepa Evropa.

490
00:20:31,619 --> 00:20:33,259
[SPEAKER_00] Skladna Evropa.

491
00:20:33,259 --> 00:20:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ništa na zemlji ne može biti

492
00:20:35,380 --> 00:20:36,339
[SPEAKER_00] dugo skladno.

493
00:20:36,339 --> 00:20:36,859
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

494
00:20:36,859 --> 00:20:38,440
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što imamo lopova

495
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] i ako mi nismo budni,

496
00:20:40,039 --> 00:20:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] ako mi ne čuvamo

497
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:42,359
[SPEAKER_00] naše temelje,

498
00:20:42,359 --> 00:20:43,140
[SPEAKER_00] naše biće,

499
00:20:43,140 --> 00:20:43,859
[SPEAKER_00] naše srce,

500
00:20:43,859 --> 00:20:44,779
[SPEAKER_00] našu dušu,

501
00:20:45,140 --> 00:20:47,099
[SPEAKER_00] evo ti njega on prokopava.

502
00:20:47,099 --> 00:20:48,180
[SPEAKER_00] I evo,

503
00:20:48,180 --> 00:20:50,420
[SPEAKER_00] zato je važno,

504
00:20:50,420 --> 00:20:51,940
[SPEAKER_00] kaže Ivan Pavao II,

505
00:20:51,940 --> 00:20:54,619
[SPEAKER_00] volio je govoriti o nedjelji.

506
00:20:56,859 --> 00:21:00,140
[SPEAKER_00] Brinite se da se svijet ne ohladi,

507
00:21:00,140 --> 00:21:01,240
[SPEAKER_00] kaže Papa.

508
00:21:01,240 --> 00:21:04,799
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite da se ne smrznete

509
00:21:04,799 --> 00:21:07,940
[SPEAKER_00] u sebičnosti i konkurentskoj borbi,

510
00:21:07,940 --> 00:21:11,500
[SPEAKER_00] u praznom hodu zaposlenosti

511
00:21:11,500 --> 00:21:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] i lova za užicima.

512
00:21:13,119 --> 00:21:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] Pričite u uskrsnoj vatri

513
00:21:16,039 --> 00:21:16,940
[SPEAKER_00] sve te mise

514
00:21:16,940 --> 00:21:19,759
[SPEAKER_00] i ne dajte da se iskvari nedjelja.

515
00:21:19,759 --> 00:21:21,680
[SPEAKER_00] Dan, gospodnji.

516
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] Dane u tjednu možemo zamisliti

517
00:21:24,380 --> 00:21:26,240
[SPEAKER_00] kao vagone željeznice,

518
00:21:26,839 --> 00:21:29,059
[SPEAKER_00] a nedjelju kao lokomotivu

519
00:21:29,059 --> 00:21:31,380
[SPEAKER_00] koja pokreće sve vagone

520
00:21:31,380 --> 00:21:32,859
[SPEAKER_00] sve dane u tjednu.

521
00:21:32,859 --> 00:21:35,660
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, volio bih,

522
00:21:35,660 --> 00:21:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] znam da se u ovoj zajednici moli,

523
00:21:37,519 --> 00:21:39,279
[SPEAKER_00] volio bih da molimo

524
00:21:39,279 --> 00:21:41,099
[SPEAKER_00] za neradnu nedjelju

525
00:21:41,099 --> 00:21:42,220
[SPEAKER_00] u našoj domovini.

526
00:21:42,220 --> 00:21:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo slobodnu domovinu

527
00:21:44,599 --> 00:21:46,319
[SPEAKER_00] i lijepu domovinu,

528
00:21:46,319 --> 00:21:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] a s druge strane

529
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] osjećamo da postoji

530
00:21:49,380 --> 00:21:50,359
[SPEAKER_00] jedno robstvo

531
00:21:50,359 --> 00:21:52,420
[SPEAKER_00] koje kao da nas želi uspavati

532
00:21:52,420 --> 00:21:54,740
[SPEAKER_00] na način da su ljudi nezadovoljni.

533
00:21:55,119 --> 00:21:57,460
[SPEAKER_00] jer kažu, pa moram i nedjeljom raditi,

534
00:21:57,460 --> 00:21:58,559
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda nisam doma,

535
00:21:58,559 --> 00:22:00,339
[SPEAKER_00] i onda neke stvari,

536
00:22:00,339 --> 00:22:01,839
[SPEAKER_00] neke špage pucaju.

537
00:22:01,839 --> 00:22:04,700
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, moramo moliti

538
00:22:04,700 --> 00:22:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] da vršimo Božje zapovjedi,

539
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:09,339
[SPEAKER_00] jer Božje zapovjedi nisu naše zapovjedi.

540
00:22:10,119 --> 00:22:13,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ili imam još malo vremena?

541
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ima još vremena?

542
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:18,140
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite,

543
00:22:18,140 --> 00:22:20,279
[SPEAKER_00] koji je put

544
00:22:20,279 --> 00:22:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] da bismo mi živjeli

545
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:23,299
[SPEAKER_00] Božje zapovjedi?

546
00:22:23,299 --> 00:22:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] Biti online,

547
00:22:26,599 --> 00:22:29,759
[SPEAKER_00] biti povezan s Isusom Kristom.

548
00:22:29,759 --> 00:22:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] Koja je najjača veza

549
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:34,900
[SPEAKER_00] naše povezanosti s Isusom?

550
00:22:34,900 --> 00:22:39,299
[SPEAKER_00] Sveta misa.

551
00:22:39,299 --> 00:22:42,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim, i sad izmislio ove neke signale,

552
00:22:42,480 --> 00:22:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] tek u zadnje vrijeme.

553
00:22:43,519 --> 00:22:45,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sveta misa

554
00:22:45,299 --> 00:22:48,240
[SPEAKER_00] je najsnažniji signal

555
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:49,700
[SPEAKER_00] između nas i Boga,

556
00:22:49,700 --> 00:22:50,460
[SPEAKER_00] zato što nam

557
00:22:50,460 --> 00:22:52,579
[SPEAKER_00] po njoj sam Bog dolazi,

558
00:22:52,579 --> 00:22:54,220
[SPEAKER_00] sam Isus dolazi

559
00:22:54,220 --> 00:22:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] među nas.

560
00:22:55,960 --> 00:22:57,299
[SPEAKER_00] I sveta misa,

561
00:22:57,299 --> 00:23:00,839
[SPEAKER_00] kada ulazimo srcem u svetu misu,

562
00:23:00,839 --> 00:23:02,099
[SPEAKER_00] sveta misa nas budi,

563
00:23:02,099 --> 00:23:03,200
[SPEAKER_00] budi našu vjeru.

564
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,519
[SPEAKER_00] Kada svećenik moli,

565
00:23:04,519 --> 00:23:07,200
[SPEAKER_00] blagosvensi gospodine Bože svega svijeta,

566
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:09,519
[SPEAKER_00] tada ti u kalež,

567
00:23:09,519 --> 00:23:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] u onaj kruh,

568
00:23:10,980 --> 00:23:13,299
[SPEAKER_00] trebaš staviti svoje molitve.

569
00:23:13,299 --> 00:23:14,980
[SPEAKER_00] Evo Isuse, donosim ti to.

570
00:23:14,980 --> 00:23:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] Donosim ti svoje brige,

571
00:23:16,599 --> 00:23:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] svoje roditelje,

572
00:23:17,619 --> 00:23:19,700
[SPEAKER_00] onaj neuspjeh u školi,

573
00:23:19,700 --> 00:23:20,920
[SPEAKER_00] što sam se zbrukao,

574
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:22,579
[SPEAKER_00] što mi nije ispalo ovo ili ono.

575
00:23:22,579 --> 00:23:24,119
[SPEAKER_00] I stavljam to.

576
00:23:24,119 --> 00:23:25,579
[SPEAKER_00] I kada, vidite,

577
00:23:25,779 --> 00:23:26,839
[SPEAKER_00] svećenik moli

578
00:23:26,839 --> 00:23:29,279
[SPEAKER_00] po Hristu i s Hristom i u Hristu,

579
00:23:29,279 --> 00:23:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] tada Bog Otac

580
00:23:30,559 --> 00:23:32,279
[SPEAKER_00] vidi

581
00:23:32,279 --> 00:23:36,099
[SPEAKER_00] tvoju molitvu u krvi i tijelu svoga Sina.

582
00:23:36,099 --> 00:23:37,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može ne vidjeti,

583
00:23:37,599 --> 00:23:38,839
[SPEAKER_00] zato što je Isus

584
00:23:38,839 --> 00:23:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] skupo za nas platio,

585
00:23:41,019 --> 00:23:42,759
[SPEAKER_00] da bi nas u nebo doveo.

586
00:23:42,759 --> 00:23:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] I zato trebamo biti budni.

587
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:46,680
[SPEAKER_00] I zato nas do šaše,

588
00:23:46,680 --> 00:23:47,700
[SPEAKER_00] potiče,

589
00:23:47,700 --> 00:23:49,079
[SPEAKER_00] da budemo budni.

590
00:23:49,079 --> 00:23:50,579
[SPEAKER_00] I na kraju

591
00:23:50,579 --> 00:23:54,140
[SPEAKER_00] tijel bih podijeliti s vama

592
00:23:54,140 --> 00:23:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] kako biti budan

593
00:23:55,599 --> 00:23:56,700
[SPEAKER_00] ovih dana,

594
00:23:56,700 --> 00:23:59,400
[SPEAKER_00] jako nas je dobro potaknuo Papa Franjo,

595
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:03,140
[SPEAKER_00] koji je 1.12. bio u Greću.

596
00:24:03,140 --> 00:24:05,259
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo je svetište Jaslica.

597
00:24:05,259 --> 00:24:08,460
[SPEAKER_00] I napisao je jedno pismo tog dana,

598
00:24:08,460 --> 00:24:09,980
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno objavio pismo,

599
00:24:09,980 --> 00:24:12,319
[SPEAKER_00] Admirabile signum.

600
00:24:12,859 --> 00:24:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] To znači čudesni znak.

601
00:24:15,380 --> 00:24:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] Čudesni znak Jaslica.

602
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:19,440
[SPEAKER_00] Papa Franjo piše,

603
00:24:19,440 --> 00:24:24,259
[SPEAKER_00] Jaslice su poput živog evanđelja,

604
00:24:24,259 --> 00:24:27,920
[SPEAKER_00] koje izobilno teče sa stranica svetog pisma.

605
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:31,099
[SPEAKER_00] Bog nas toliko ljubi,

606
00:24:31,099 --> 00:24:33,359
[SPEAKER_00] da je postao jedno s nama,

607
00:24:33,359 --> 00:24:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] kako bismo i mi

608
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:37,240
[SPEAKER_00] postali jedno s njime.

609
00:24:37,240 --> 00:24:40,740
[SPEAKER_00] Porijeklo Jaslica nalazimo

610
00:24:40,740 --> 00:24:41,559
[SPEAKER_00] prije svega

